## SafeExecutorResult type

Represents the result of a safe execution, either successful or failed.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export type SafeExecutorResult<T, E = unknown> = T extends Promise<infer U> ? Promise<SafeResult<U, E>> : SafeResult<T, E>;
```
